Privacy Notice for Digital Platforms
v. Your Privacy Choices
v. Your Privacy Choices
We invite you to adjust the privacy settings of your browser and/or device in order to control what information is automatically tracked about you. You can click on the links below to find out how to do so:
Google Chrome
Mozilla Firefox
Microsoft Edge
Opera
Apple Safari for Mac
Apple Safari for iPhone and iPad
Apple iPhone Privacy Settings
Google Android Privacy Settings
If you choose to download a cookie blocker, please note that it will stop some of our products from working properly, or entirely, on your device. More specifically, your access to audio and video content, location-based services, search features, registration, sign-in and commenting may be affected.
In addition, CBC/Radio-Canada is a member of the Digital Advertising Alliance of Canada (DAAC) and adheres to its principles. By visiting the web page of
DAAC
, you can opt-out of targeted advertising by multiple companies, including CBC/Radio-Canada.
Cookie Notice
We and select advertising partners use trackers to collect some of your data in order to enhance your experience and to deliver personalized content and advertising. If you are not comfortable with the use of this information, please
review your device and browser privacy settings
before continuing your visit.
